Service Level Objectives terminology
Error budget
Amount of acceptable errors
Implementace pomocí Promethea
sum(rate(http_requests_total{app="foo", status!~"5.."}[1h]))
/
sum(rate(http_requests_total{app="foo"}[1h])
slo:error_ratio1h
Implementace pomocí Promethea
slo:error_ratio1h{app="foo"} > (14.4*0.001)
and
slo:error_ratio5m{job="myjob"} > (14.4*0.001)
or
slo:error_ratio6h{job="myjob"} > (6*0.001)
and
slo:error_ratio30m{job="myjob"} > (6*0.001)
